{"tid":1754210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位我地未贏嫁！開心完要繼續抗爭呀！","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:38:26.000Z","uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10825abc2bc82de575a235baef245856abf3e1d2","tid":1754210,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"區選贏咁多我真係好撚開心，班仆街建制終於食番惡果<br />\n<br />\n但係我地未贏嫁，大家一齊睇下林鄭條仆街點講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「她又說，昨日的投票日大致在和平、安全和有序的情況下進行，經過過去5個多月的社會動盪，深信絕大部分市民和她一樣，希望和平、安全和有序的情況可以持續。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n條仆街既說法又想spin落<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「暴力」</span></span>呢個話題上面，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">扮</span></strong></span>企係我地同一個立場去尋求我地既同意。<br />\n<br />\n仆街政棍既說法聽得多就好易洗腦，雖然大家心水清，但我都想提提大家！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好比班政棍呃到</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>解散警隊，刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n現時最重要既係：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">解救Poly圍城！譴責黑警侵犯人權！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a2b5a7e4449151fa52ca1f0dabc60b7a89f27a76","tid":1754210,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[元朗屏山北][搞大佢]區選仲未完仲可以再爭取!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754167</a>"}]}